data.title: Innovation Zero
data.text:
Welcome to the 2024 content programme! With over 200 CPD certified sessions taking place across 14 dedicated forums, including Energy, Finance, Food & Agriculture, Industrial, Transport, Advanced Tech, Aviation & Shipping, Built Environment, and Carbon Markets, this event is essential for anyone looking to keep up with the latest trends, investment opportunities, and announcements.
